[[Jeremy Castro Baguyos|Jeremy Baguyos]] (University of Nebraska at Omaha, USA)
Tim Blackwell (Goldsmiths College, Great Britain),
George Bloch (Composer, France),
Marc Chemiller (IRCAM/CNRS, France),
