This is a '''list of companies of Canada''', businesses operating out of [[Canada]], [[Incorporation (business)|incorporated]] in Canada, or [[Multinational corporation|multinational companies]] with divisions located in Canada. This list excludes companies doing business in or with Canada which do not have articles of incorporation for a branch or division within Canada. This list does include past or defunct businesses.
{{dynamic list}}

