*[[The Economist]] (60th Floor)
*[[Swiss Reinsurance Company]] (37th and 67th Floor)
{{Expand section|date=June 2008}}
* [http://www.conshongkong.esteri.it/Consolato_HongKong] Italian Consulate 32nd Floor

