| Image = Pap smear showing clamydia in the vacuoles 500x H&amp;E.jpg
| Caption = Pap smear showing ''C. trachomatis'' (H&amp;E stain)
| ICD10 = {{ICD10|A|55||a|50}}-{{ICD10|A|56|8|a|50}}, {{ICD10|A|70||a|70}}-{{ICD10|A|74|9|a|70}} 
